get":{"id":499048567,"title":"法国总统马克龙修改了国旗颜色，却并未公开宣布，此举有何影响？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/499048567","type":"question","created":1636956283,"answer_count":360,"follower_count":2327,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[704,179071,181998,1407417],"comment_count":73,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"英国广播公司14日报道称，法国总统马克龙悄悄修改了法国国旗的颜色。就在去年（2020年），法国总统府已经悬挂上了带有新色调的旗帜，但并没有向外界宣布。 法国官员向媒体透露，马克龙已将法国国旗三块颜色中的蓝色进行修改，用色调更深的海军蓝取代了原先较亮的颜色。外媒称，新的颜色是法国大革命的象征。 报道称，事实上，无论是更深的蓝色还是较浅的蓝色都已经使用了几十年。法国海军和许多官方的建筑都一直使用海军蓝，但在1976年，在时任法国总统吉斯卡尔·德斯坦的领导下，法国政府在三色旗上使用更亮的蓝色，这在一定程度上是出于审美考虑。 爱丽舍宫尚未公开宣布更换旗帜，也未下令其它机构也这样做。马克龙这一决定也引发了舆论分歧，一些人认为新的颜色影响美观。"},"attached_info":"Cj8I8/yshbWy7uA1EAMaCDczMTgxMDAyIPvwx4wGMEk4lxJAAnIJNDk5MDQ4NTY3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"736 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-e7fcab6e16875bb191fca26179676e93.jpeg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"3_1637039270.9457285","card_id":"Q_306052528","target":{"id":306052528,"title":"为什么李商隐的很多诗题目都为《无题》？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/306052528","type":"question","created":1545050875,"answer_count":35,"follower_count":219,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2058,4579,5086,11524,208101],"comment_count":3,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I8/yshbWy7uA1EAMaCDMwMjg3ODYxIPu13uAFMAM42wFAA3IJMzA2MDUyNTI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"638 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-ed6cc21159f1bb2ad8ef2836de5e7d0c_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"4_1637039270.9461946","card_id":"Q_498200987","target":{"id":498200987,"title":"月薪 2 万以上的人是不是无法想象月薪 2 千的人是